quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  32,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  32,1,Alif Laaam Meeam
  32,2,is mein kuch shak nahi ke is kitaab ka nazilkiya jana tamam Jahan ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se hai
  32,3,kiya yeh log yeh kehte hain ke paighambar ne is ko az khud bana liya hai ( nahi ) balkay woh tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se brhq hai taakay tum un logon ko hadaayat karo jin ke paas tum se pehlay koi hadaayat karne wala nahi aaya taakay yeh raste par chalein
  32,4,khuda hi to hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo cheeze un dono mein hain sab ko chay din mein pedakiya phir arsh par ja thehra. is ke siwa nah tumhara koi dost hai aur nah sifarish karne wala.kiya tum nasiyaat nahi pakarte ?
  32,5,wohi aasman se zameen taq ( ke ) har kaam ka intizam karta hai. phir woh aik roz jis ki miqdaar tumahray shumaar ke mutabiq hazaar baras hogi. is ki taraf Saood ( aur rujoo ) kere ga
  32,6,yahi to posheeda aur zahir ka jan-nay wala ( aur ) ghalib aur reham wala ( khuda ) hai
  32,7,jis ne har cheez ko bohat achi terhan banaya ( yani ) is ko pedakiya. aur ensaan ki paidaiesh ko matti se shurukiya
  32,8,phir is ki nasal khlase se ( yani ) haqeer pani se peda ki
  32,9,phir uss ko durustkiya phir is mein apni ( taraf se ) rooh phonki aur tumahray kaan aur ankhen aur dil banaye magar tum bohat kam shukar karte ho
  32,10,aur kehnay lagey ke jab hum zameen mein malyamait ho jaien ge tokiya az sar e no peda hon ge. haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh log apne perwar-digaar ke samnay jaane hi ke qaail nahi
  32,11,keh do ke mout ka farishta jo tum par muqarrarkiya gaya hai tumhari roohein qabz kar laita hai phir tum apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout’tay jao ge
  32,12,aur tum ( taajjub karo ) jab dekho ke gunehgaar apne perwar-digaar ke samnay sar jhukaye hon ge ( aur kahin ge ke ) ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ne dekh liya aur sun liya to hum ko ( duniya mein ) wapas bhaij day ke naik amal karen bay shak hum yaqeen karne walay hain
  32,13,aur agar hum chahtay to har shakhs ko hadaayat day dete. lekin meri taraf se yeh baat qarar pachki hai ke mein dozakh ko junoo aur insanon sab se bhar do ga
  32,14,so ( ab aag ke ) mazay chako is liye ke tum ne uss din ke anay ko bhala rakha tha ( aaj ) hum bhi tumhe bhala den ge aur jo kaam tum karte they unn ki saza mein hamesha ke azaab ke mazay chahkte raho
  32,15,hamari aayton par to wohi log imaan laatay hain ke jab unn ko unn se nasiyaat ki jati hai to sjday mein girr parrtay aur apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karte hain aur ghuroor nahi karte
  32,16,unn ke pehlu bichonon se allag rehtay hain ( aur ) woh apne perwar-digaar ko khauf aur umeed se pkarte aur jo ( maal ) hum ne unn ko diya hai is mein se kharch karte hain
  32,17,koi mutnaqas nahi jaanta ke unn ke liye kaisi aankhon ki thandak chhupa kar rakhi gayi hai. yeh un aamaal ka sila hai jo woh karte they
  32,18,bhala jo momin ho woh is shakhs ki terhan ho sakta hai jo nafarman ho? dono barabar nahi ho satke
  32,19,jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay unn ke ( rehne ke ) liye baagh hain yeh mehmani unn kamon ki jaza hai jo woh karte they
  32,20,aur jinhon ne nafarmani ki unn ke rehne ke liye dozakh hai jab chahain ge ke is mein se nikal jayen to is mein lota diye jayen ge. aur unn se kaha jaye ga ke jis dozakh ke azaab ko tum jhoot samajte they is ke mazay chako
  32,21,aur hum unn ko ( qayamat ke ) barray azaab ke siwa azaab duniya ka bhi maza chkhayin ge. shayad ( hamari taraf ) lout ayen
  32,22,aur is shakhs se barh kar zalim kon jis ko is ke perwar-digaar ki aayton se nasiyaat ki jaye to woh unn se munh phair le. hum gunahgaaron se zaroor badla lainay walay hain
  32,23,aur hum ne moose ko kitaab di to tum unn ke milnay se shak mein nah hona aur hum ne is ( kitaab ) ko ( ya moose ko ) bani Israel ke liye ( zareya ) hadaayat banaya
  32,24,aur un mein se hum ne peshwa banaye they jo hamaray hukum se hadaayatkiya karte they. jab woh sabr karte they aur woh hamari aayton par yaqeen rakhtay they
  32,25,bilashuba tumhara perwar-digaar un mein jin baton mein woh ikhtilaaf karte they. qayamat ke roz faisla kar day ga
  32,26,kiya unn ko is ( amar ) se hadaayat nah hui ke hum ne unn se pehlay bohat si amtoN ko jin ke maqamat sukoonat mein yeh chaltay phirtay hain halaak kar diya. bay shak is mein nishanain hain. to yeh suntay kyun nahi
  32,27,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke hum banjar zameen ki taraf pani rawan karte hain phir is se khaiti peda karte hain jis mein se un ke chopaye bhi khatay hain aur woh khud bhi ( khatay hain ) to yeh dekhte kyun nahi .
  32,28,aur kehte hain agar tum sachey ho to yeh faisla kab hoga ?
  32,29,keh do ke faislay ke din kafiroon ko un ka imaan lana kuch bhi faida nah day ga aur nah unn ko mohlat di jaye gi
  32,30,to unn se munh phair lau aur intzaar karo yeh bhi intzaar kar rahay hain
